snippet.title: Astral Doorway
snippet.description:
The purpose of this channel is to spread awareness about the reality and practice of awakening consciousness through deep meditation, yoga, astral projection, and more; ultimately guiding us all closer to our own specific 'Path of Inner Initiation into the Greater Mysteries of Reality... and Beyond Reality!'

To do this, we learn practical wisdom to begin gaining our own "Gnosis" (knowledge from direct experience as opposed to mere beliefs). There are many videos that cover a range of topics, go to the 'Playlists' section and choose where you want to begin.

If you want to donate, you can join the Discord group for live Q&As, early-access episodes, forums & more. This also helps others by supporting the channel: https://www.patreon.com/astraldoorway üôè
